Title: Inception
StoryLine: A thief enters the dreams of others to steal their secrets.

Title: The Shawshank Redemption
StoryLine: Two imprisoned men bond over years, finding solace and eventual redemption.

Title: Pulp Fiction
StoryLine: Various interconnected stories of crime in Los Angeles.

Title: The Dark Knight
StoryLine: Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

Title: Forrest Gump
StoryLine: The life journey of a man with a low IQ but good intentions.

Title: The Matrix
StoryLine: A computer hacker learns about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.

Title: Schindler's List
StoryLine: In German-occupied Poland during World War II, industrialist Oskar Schindler gradually becomes concerned for his Jewish workforce.

Title: Fight Club
StoryLine: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soapmaker form an underground fight club.

Title: The Godfather
StoryLine: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.

Title: Titanic
StoryLine: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

Title: Inglourious Basterds
StoryLine: In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a plan to assassinate Nazi leaders by a group of Jewish U.S. soldiers coincides with a theatre owner's vengeful plans for the same.
